					<div class="box-1 mb-30">
						<h3 class="heading-4 mb-20">矯正治療の流れ　目次</h3>
						<ul>
							<li class="mb-10 indent-2"><a href="#flow-1" class="heading-3 _page-link">1- xxx</a></li>
